        "id": "docling_exam_paper_en-file-putnam-archive_2010_Solutions_2010s_page_001_2",
        "observed_type": "list_item",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "A-1 The largest such k is |\"7 J = [4]. For n even, this value is achieved by the partition",
        "bbox": [
