      {
        "id": "docling_exam_paper_en-file-putnam-archive_2010_Solutions_2010s_page_001_17",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Since 10\" > n ≥ 2\" ≥m + 1, 10\" is divisible by 2\" and hence by 2m+1, and similarly 1010\" is divisible by 210\" and hence by 2m+1. It follows that",
        "bbox": [
          0.5543462424331795,
