        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Define the function g : R → R by g(x) = f(x+ 1) f(x), and put c = g(0), d = f(0). For all x E R, 8' (x) = f(x + 1) - f(x) = 0, so g(x) = c identically, and f(x) = f(x+1) - f(x) = g(x) =c, so f(x) = cx+d identically as desired.",
        "bbox": [
